You can purchase a pass for a great fitness center with steam room and lap pool.	You can walk down to Pike Market in minutes.	For $8 I upgraded my room to a corner room with couch/sitting area.	And although we didn't take advantage, a different winery does a tasting in the lobby for guests every afternoon.	It had room for a stack of dumb bells, a bike, treadmill and eliptical.	Great chance for those traveling alone to converse with others.)	A very nice touch with the hot apple cider/coffee tea.	Our room had a queen size bed, a small bathroom, small closet & desk; sufficient for a short stay.